  "text": "## Business Continuity  \n**Branch Closure Procedures:**\n- 30-day customer notice required\n- Customer data transfer support\n- Alternative branch assignment\n- Digital services promotion  \n**Disaster Recovery:**\n- Banking services rerouted to nearest branch\n- Customer data secured in off-site backup\n- Communication plan activation\n- Regular BCP testing (annual)  \n**See:** Business Continuity Plan (BCP-001)  \n---",
